reviewText: Hard to find but easy to get here. Thank you. You made my wife and baby girl really happy

To the one star reviewers. You know why they don't play in your dvd player? Because they are Blu Ray.

Ill help you out tho. You know where else they won't play? VCRs, laserdisc players, cd players, cassette decks, 8- track units, not even beta max players. You know why? Because again, like the title states, they are Blu Ray discs.

It amazes me how you people make it through life here on planet earth.  Exactly why the rating system is screwed up on amazon. Stupidity. Fun bonus fact, diesel won't work in your gas car either. One star for diesel!
